      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that still looks great in the driveway! It runs smoothly and has been well-cared for over the years. I'd love to see it go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
