    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanical integrity is prioritized with a documented VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles the 50/50 weight distribution as intended. The suspension maintains its composure through corners with refreshed bushings and dampers. While showing minor signs of road use, the paint retains a deep gloss and the interior leather remains supple. This is a mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the canyon or the track.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
