    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained driver. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish that shines beautifully in the sunlight, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small, superficial scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and impressively clean. The premium upholstery shows light character creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster but remains free of tears or stains, while the dashboard and touchpoints are in excellent shape with all buttons and infotainment features functioning perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly with no unexpected vibrations or leaks. The transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension feels tight and responsive over bumps. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a multi-point inspection confirming that the brakes and tires have significant life left. This is a solid, honest car that has been kept in a condition that any owner would be proud of.",
